  "contentHtml": "<p class=\"p\" style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:33px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;color:#333333;font-size:19px;background:#ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;根据《普通高等学校学生管理规定》（教育部令第</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">41号）、《福建省教育厅关于做好普通高等学校学生转学备案工作的通知》(闽教学〔2017〕46号)和《福建中医药大学学年学分制学籍管理实施细则</span></span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">（修订稿）</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;color:#333333;font-size:19px;background:#ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">》</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">(校办〔2019〕26号)的规定，经</span></span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;color:#333333;font-size:19px;background:#ffffff;font-family:仿宋;\">林圣杰</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;color:#333333;font-size:19px;background:#ffffff;font-family:仿宋;\">同学本人申请，</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;color:#333333;font-size:19px;background:#ffffff;font-family:仿宋;\">药</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;color:#333333;font-size:19px;background:#ffffff;font-family:仿宋;\">学院初核，教务处审核，同意其转学（转出）。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:37px;line-height:33px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px;\">现将</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;color:#333333;font-size:19px;background:#ffffff;font-family:仿宋;\">林圣杰</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;color:#333333;font-size:19px;background:#ffffff;font-family:仿宋;\">同</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px;\">学转学（转出）情况予以公示（详见附件），公示期：</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px;\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px;\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">-</span></span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px;\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:19px;\">月</span><span st